#

Ranch Burger

25 min
$12
650 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinComfort Food

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyQuickBurger

Description

A juicy beef burger topped with creamy ranch dressing and fresh toppings, delivering a burst of flavor in every bite.

Ingredients

  • ground beef: 1 lb
  • burger buns: 4
  • ranch dressing: 1/2 cup
  • lettuce: 4 leaves
  • tomato: 1, sliced
  • cheddar cheese: 4 slices
  • pickles: 1/2 cup
  • olive oil: 1 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
